items.bio: Property Consultant at DMCI Homes. Papa's Babygirl. Sweetest creature. Soon to be Entrepreneur. Servant of God.

Its really hard to keep afloat in a world that is sinking more and more each day,

but i have managed to survive because i am a survivor.
hated by many .. confronted by none 😄😄😄
No one wants to handle me.

Rather look good in person than on pictures... :p
